'''Jack Thompson''' is an Australian actor who played [[Cliegg Lars]] in [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']]. He was born on [[August 31]], [[1940s#1940|1940]],<ref name="SW Mando S2" /> and his birth name was John Hadley Pain.

